&lt;p&gt;·&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;a href="https://docs.aws.amazon.com/workspaces/latest/adminguide/wsp-pools-end-of-support.html"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Amazon WorkSpaces - Pool&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;·&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;a href="https://docs.aws.amazon.com/managedservices/latest/userguide/SunsetPlan"&gt;&lt;b&gt;AWS Managed Services (AMS) Advanced&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;·&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;a href="https://docs.aws.amazon.com/repostprivate/latest/userguide/repost-private-end-of-support.html"&gt;&lt;b&gt;AWS re:Post Private&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;·&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;a href="https://docs.aws.amazon.com/sagemaker/latest/dg/profiler-availability-change.html"&gt;Amazon Sagemaker AI- Profiler&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; 
